Locial Network's update version of this amazing WP-Capistrano Tool.
Changes are specific to LocialNetwork's individual development.

This is a vanilla WordPress 4.1 install, set up for easy deployment using Capistrano, git, wp-cli and sed.

For more instruction, check out http://vimeo.com/72087167
For more instruction, check out http://www.metaltoad.com/blog/tutorial-simplify-your-wordpress-deployments

Updated instructions: https://github.com/kronda/basewp

IMPORTANT: Be sure to modify everything in config/ before attempting Capistrano deployments
